The paper presents a new variable actuation mechanism based on a parallel robot, which falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the kinematics and singularity analysis of the robot, which can be categorized under mechanical engineering (cs.ME) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also presents a novel design for the robot, which can be categorized under robotics (cs.ROB) and robotics and automation (cs.ROBOC).
